{"about_the_game":"<strong>This 45-minute gameplay demo will allow you to familiarize yourself with the full game mechanics by adopting 4 unique capybaras in your park. We'll be updating the demo regularly to resolve any bugs or problems you may encounter during gameplay, so don't hesitate to let us know.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/Separator.png?t=1724920531\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Full Game Features</strong></h2>Relax in this peaceful game and take care of your favorite little residents: capybaras! Create menus that meet their needs, keep them happy and grow your park<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Enjoy a cozy game</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/Separator.png?t=1724920531\" /><br>Do as the capybaras do, make yourself comfortable and have a good time. There's no time pressure<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/GIF_01.gif?t=1724920531\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build and decorate your own park</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/Separator.png?t=1724920531\" /><br>Design and decorate your capybara's enclosures with care. Unlock new decorative and comfort features to enhance your capybara's well-being.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/GIF_02.gif?t=1724920531\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Adapt to the specific needs of each capybara</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125960/extras/Separator.png?t=1724920531\" /><br>Each capybara has its own needs, grows its own food and carefully chooses the composition of its plate to enhance its well-being with an addictive mini-game inspired by inventory management ga